{"tid":51420,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[麻甩食堂] 簡易麻婆豆腐","createTime":"2016-12-23T08:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T17:04:00.000Z","uid":66774,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c94db2f72e8d59f68efdd7bf83d7f7d4da3cce8","tid":51420,"uid":66774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"自己一個人 出街食又唔知食乜<br />\n諗住自己煮時 上網睇食譜見到人地淨係香料材料到十鳩幾種 睇見到麻煩<br />\n由其係bob叔條撚樣 架餐又多又高級 <br />\n香料數埋都廿鳩幾種 叫我地呢d麻甩佬去邊到搵 真係幫佢含撚都唔得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">佢係我偶像來</span></span><br />\n所以希望可以同各位分享下不同簡單又好食既食譜<br />\n簡化得來又不失風味 亦保留到道菜最主要既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jwok10eu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjwok10eu&h=5b0ea1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先準備材料<br />\n薑蒜求鳩其切碎 <br />\n軟豆腐一磚切粒放入鹽水浸住佢<br />\n免治豬肉 $5-10 視乎你想食幾多肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aoyzswpd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faoyzswpd&h=a2f19b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文火爆香薑蒜末大約一兩分鐘到你聞到香味<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tk0pc7uh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftk0pc7uh&h=7dfa5c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入辣豆瓣醬 兩大匙 再爆香一分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6vjh1e4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6vjh1e4&h=c951d51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入豬肉炒至六成熟<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qiunb16k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqiunb16k&h=88a4208c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入半碗水或雞湯等滾起<br />\n滾起後加入小小老抽 糖 後試味<br />\n呢個時候如果各位有私家辣椒油麻辣醬可以加入少許去調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vpbx94a2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvpbx94a2&h=4578f734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入豆腐後千其唔撚好大力炒<br />\n要溫柔咁去翻滾肉碎同豆腐 或者輕輕搖動隻pan<br />\n令所有豆腐都沾上醬汁後 中火煮2-3分鐘收汁同煮濃<br />\n再加入小量生粉水 煮到個汁好似一日第三篤精咁 半稀杰狀態 再轉大火煮半分鐘 之後就可以上碟啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rto4dfuq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frto4dfuq&h=6cb2f323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟前可以加上適當葱花 不"},{"pid":"9f71938e63602546795715d89745c25569ce8943","tid":51420,"uid":66774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:08:00.000Z","msg":"[quote]自己一個人 出街食又唔知食乜<br />\n諗住自己煮時 上網睇食譜見到人地淨係香料材料到十鳩幾種 睇見到麻煩<br />\n由其係bob叔條撚樣 架餐又多又高級 <br />\n香料數埋都廿鳩幾種 叫我地呢d麻甩佬去邊到搵 真係幫佢含撚都唔得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">佢係我偶像來</span></span><br />\n所以希望可以同各位分享下不同簡單又好食既食譜<br />\n簡化得來又不失風味 亦保留到道菜最主要既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jwok10eu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjwok10eu&h=5b0ea1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先準備材料<br />\n薑蒜求鳩其切碎 <br />\n軟豆腐一磚切粒放入鹽水浸住佢<br />\n免治豬肉 $5-10 視乎你想食幾多肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aoyzswpd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faoyzswpd&h=a2f19b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文火爆香薑蒜末大約一兩分鐘到你聞到香味<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tk0pc7uh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftk0pc7uh&h=7dfa5c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入辣豆瓣醬 兩大匙 再爆香一分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o6vjh1e4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo6vjh1e4&h=c951d51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入豬肉炒至六成熟<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qiunb16k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqiunb16k&h=88a4208c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入半碗水或雞湯等滾起<br />\n滾起後加入小小老抽 糖 後試味<br />\n呢個時候如果各位有私家辣椒油麻辣醬可以加入少許去調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vpbx94a2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvpbx94a2&h=4578f734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入豆腐後千其唔撚好大力炒<br />\n要溫柔咁去翻滾肉碎同豆腐 或者輕輕搖動隻pan<br />\n令所有豆腐都沾上醬汁後 中火煮2-3分鐘收汁同煮濃<br />\n再加入小量生粉水 煮到個汁好似一日第三篤精咁 半稀杰狀態 再轉大火煮半分鐘 之後就可以上碟啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rto4dfuq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frto4dfuq&h=6cb2f323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟前可以加上適當葱花 不過我唔食蔥 所以無加<br />\n屌未打哂就hi錯制post左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35309ebb97129c1bbdbcd71b5e3d53f3992d09c","tid":51420,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4bf0b34d952b577fbd0178d6d1ac31f7f89e8ff","tid":51420,"uid":66774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"以上係小麻小辣版本<br />\n中意麻既巴打可以上碟前加入已磨碎花椒粒去提高麻辣感<br />\n或者好似我咁加花椒油或麻辣醬去代替花椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想辣d就可以加入幾條切碎辣椒仔<br />\n切碎豆腐後浸起鹽水可以增加其硬度同口感<br />\n正宗麻婆豆腐講求麻辣色香燙<br />\n麻味就靠花椒油或麻辣醬or磨碎花椒粒<br />\n辣味就靠豆瓣醬同辣椒<br />\n色就靠少許既老抽<br />\n香味就靠爆香既薑蒜同醬料<br />\n燙就係加上碟前既大火加熱半分鐘去提高熱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8764fc10c6b330b91bf13b5e909e97a14284ad","tid":51420,"uid":66774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都成日煮呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我落豆瓣醬</blockquote><br />\n我都有落豆瓣醬呀 不過我嫌味道唔夠豐富加左自己既辣椒醬同麻辣醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d497c7e8c7847dfae682c6af4f9707d679a2a5e6","tid":51420,"uid":35340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebc56d29c2da56ff5babd36d55b30c78ad5654d","tid":51420,"uid":66774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b3810153216ad81030eef097804f7f19a6689d","tid":51420,"uid":11680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0108073a37a845118dee4edac0a8b78c91a7c396","tid":51420,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:42:32.000Z","msg":"放假煮來試試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef79b8e79dd5b02bcdbbe635c12bed75997fd9d","tid":51420,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ca675276a4a0d72855cbed28ba39bf6b21f735e0","tid":51420,"uid":3594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"成日煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送飯一流"},{"pid":"126c8ffd575707221896f3b7f9dee678f0785877","tid":51420,"uid":16131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"麻婆豆腐 魚香茄子 涼瓜牛肉<br />\n麻甩必食"},{"pid":"1cb076667fb3a5dbcd039155c67a58e2c23b0e2b","tid":51420,"uid":8727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"好波 我自己仲意食辣到仆街果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f6ba34fbb17cf356bfe6b8b7aa0c52c0a38643","tid":51420,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"真係好撚易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1caa91dd87a247103c957b2bed606b945b4bb14","tid":51420,"uid":11792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"一直想整麻婆豆腐, 不過見食譜要勁多料所以冇整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒有機會會跟巴打食譜煮一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a360d918a1388833b27712d26661692feb281b14","tid":51420,"uid":44780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直想整麻婆豆腐, 不過見食譜要勁多料所以冇整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒有機會會跟巴打食譜煮一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都叫多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"68bcc03447f70b1c6ed70e2cc2ff180201129426","tid":51420,"uid":11833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:48:19.000Z","msg":"要簡單買李錦記預先調好既醬料囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079b2d1e61e4263cb6ca600f6d5d80961f6df4c7","tid":51420,"uid":26918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:10:09.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打會唔會出埋其他家常小菜教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757aed7cebc40e17fd8f64f58d870c2d6cc4b4e6","tid":51420,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7bb1534570c4418b2dd35510d2ab8478ddb0a239","tid":51420,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要簡單買李錦記預先調好既醬料囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"